		public function DEVREADME() 
		{
			/*Flixel mods:
			 * =======================================
			 * In FLxG. there is a static public var tilesize this is for easy changing tilesize
			 * 
			 * FlxG class changes:
			 *     
			 * 	public class FlxG
			 *	static public var tilesize:uint=32;
			 *	static public var lives:uint = 3;
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * //ELEMENTARAMA JARGON
			 * Grp Groups for Overlaps , GrpXXX causes getXXX
			 * MGrps Meta Grps (can contain grps ^^) for collision
			 * 
			 * // KNOWN BUGS
			 * =========================================================
			 * - There's a solid Sprite in the top left corner ;)
			 * - Cycling states crashes (kill(), destroy()??)
			 * - Font Error Pause , just needs to be done, the font actually doesn't contain all letters
			 * - Error when pausing tweens 
			 * - Error when Pausing class loaded Snd like enmey1Snd , see Flixelfoum /help/snail/
			 * - Nonsolid coins VS overlap issue
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * Gameobjects
			 * ======================================================================
			 * All Gameobjects extend Flixelcode some use the Tween Class (e.g. Coins, Powerups)
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * gameobjects consist basically of 3 Parts
			 * 
			 * Image Settings
			 * ---------------
			 * This are the basic Image Settings like width height offset orientation size and animation
			 * 
			 * Collision Settings
			 * ------------------
			 * Collision Settings these must be set correctly	
			 * otherwise the enemys will get stuck on gameobjects or the bullets won't go through 'em
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			 * Groups
			 * ====================================================
			 * For Collision, there are:
			 * 
			 * _enemies
			 * _bullets
			 * _objects
			 * 
			 * And for every GameObject that interacts with the player e.g. GrpCoins GrpExit GrpPowerup
			 * 
			 * is a get
			 * 
			 * 
			 * 
			
			 FlxObject.hitRight() calls FlxObject.hitLeft() // See Flixel Forum
			 Non Solid Sprites can't collide() OR Overlap // See Flixel Forum, must be solid , no way
			 ==========================================================
		
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
			 
		 /**
		 * Call this function to remove all members of the group are dead.
		 * 
		 * @return Remove from <code>FlxGroup</code> the <code>FlxObject</code> flaged as dead.
		 */
		/*public function removeDead():void {
